tv.amwa.maj.model

Interface Dictionary

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InterchangeObject, MediaEntity, MetadataObject
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DictionaryImpl

    public interface Dictionary
extends InterchangeObject

    Specifies a container for definitions. Every AAF file has a dictionary within its preface and contains a representation of the meta dictionary.

    See Also:
    MetaDictionary, DefinitionObject, MetaDefinition, Preface.getDictionaries(), TypeDefinitions.DictionaryStrongReference

      • addDefinitions

        boolean addDefinitions(MetadataObject metadataObject)

        Scan the given metadata object to see if it contains and references to definitions not known in this dictionary, adding any missing definitions to this dictionary as it goes.

        Parameters:
        metadataObject - Metadata object to check for missing definitions.
        Returns:
        Are all definitions referenced by the given metadata object now in registered in this dictionary?

      • addDefinition

        boolean addDefinition(DefinitionObject definition)

        Add the given definition to this dictionary if it is not already contained. If the definition is already represented, this methods returns successfully.

        Parameters:
        definition - Definition to add to this dictionary.
        Returns:
        Has the given definition been added to this dictionary successfully.
